OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1783774107
OL,3,CTwo brothers facing life in jail over
OL,4,Cmurdering civil servant "for fun" in
OL,5,C1984
OL,7,FTwo brothers are facing life in jail
OL,8,Ffor killing a civil servant 42 years
OL,9,Fago during a spree of gratuitous
OL,10,Fviolence against gay men.
OL,12,FMichael Stewart, 57, and Anthony
OL,13,FStewart, 60, were just 15 and 18 when
OL,14,Fthey set upon Anthony Littler as he
OL,15,Fwalked home in East Finchley on May 1
OL,16,F1984.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/10
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,375,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1783774107
OL,3,CTwo brothers facing life in jail over
OL,4,Cmurdering civil servant "for fun" in
OL,5,C1984
OL,7,FThe victim had spent the evening at a
OL,8,Fpub in Surrey at a meeting of the
OL,9,FPonds Branch of The Society for the
OL,10,FPreservation of Beer from the Wood, a
OL,11,Fgroup interested in promoting and
OL,12,Fpreserving traditional beer.
OL,14,FHe was ambushed and left for dead as
OL,15,Fhe walked home down a narrow alleyway
OL,16,Ffrom East Finchley Tube station in the
OL,17,Fearly hours of the morning.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/10
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,375,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1783774107
OL,3,CTwo brothers facing life in jail over
OL,4,Cmurdering civil servant "for fun" in
OL,5,C1984
OL,7,FLittler was hit twice over the head
OL,8,Fwith a blunt weapon and was found
OL,9,Fmortally wounded half an hour later,
OL,10,Fstill with his briefcase, #80 cash and
OL,11,Fcredit cards.
OL,13,FWithin minutes of the attack, Michael
OL,14,FStewart had anonymously called for an
OL,15,Fambulance from a phone box, but a
OL,16,Fsearch for an injured man was called
OL,17,Foff after he hung up.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/10
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,375,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1783774107
OL,3,CTwo brothers facing life in jail over
OL,4,Cmurdering civil servant "for fun" in
OL,5,C1984
OL,7,FHalf an hour later, Littler was found
OL,8,Fby members of the public lying in a
OL,9,Fpool of blood having suffered a
OL,10,F"catastrophic" brain injury.
OL,12,FBy the spring of 1984 the Stewart
OL,13,Fsiblings and their friends had made a
OL,14,F"hobby" of targeting lone men who they
OL,15,Fbelieved to be gay, jurors were told.
OL,17,FBut during house-to-house police
OL,18,Finquiries, they claimed to be at home
OL,19,Fat the time of the attack on Littler,
OL,20,Fwith binman Anthony Stewart insisting
OL,21,Fhe never used the alley.
OL,26,@rD@AOUrD@NO]vD@AOUvD@GO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G4/10
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,375,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1783774107
OL,3,CTwo brothers facing life in jail over
OL,4,Cmurdering civil servant "for fun" in
OL,5,C1984
OL,7,FDespite an appeal on ITV's Police 5
OL,8,Fand BBC's Crimewatch, no meaningful
OL,9,Fleads were identified and the case
OL,10,Fremained unsolved for decades, the Old
OL,11,FBailey heard.
OL,13,FThe breakthrough came on the 29th
OL,14,Fanniversary of Littler's death, when
OL,15,Fthe defendants' younger brother
OL,16,FDaniel, who was 10 at the time, came
OL,17,Fforward to police after a family
OL,18,Ffalling-out.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G5/10
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,375,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1783774107
OL,3,CTwo brothers facing life in jail over
OL,4,Cmurdering civil servant "for fun" in
OL,5,C1984
OL,7,FHe told officers his older brothers
OL,8,Fhad confessed to the killing and
OL,9,Fboasted about being involved in "queer
OL,10,Fbashing", jurors were told.
OL,12,FYears after the killing, Michael
OL,13,FStewart had also admitted his guilt to
OL,14,Fa girlfriend and even showed her where
OL,15,Fit happened, the court had heard.
OL,17,FIn 2022, police reopened the
OL,18,Finvestigation and deployed covert
OL,19,Finvestigative techniques against the
OL,20,Fbrothers, bugging their cars and
OL,21,FMichael's home.
OL,26,@qD@aOUrD@HO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G6/10
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,375,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37407
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1783774107
OL,3,CTwo brothers facing life in jail over
OL,4,Cmurdering civil servant "for fun" in
OL,5,C1984
OL,7,FAnthony was said to be a man of few
OL,8,Fwords but Michael proved to have a
OL,9,F"loose tongue" and bragged about what
OL,10,Fhe did in 1984, the court heard.
OL,12,FBoth defendants, from north London,
OL,13,Fwho declined to give evidence, had
OL,14,Fdenied involvement.
OL,16,FAn Old Bailey jury deliberated for
OL,17,Fless than three hours to find them
OL,18,Fguilty of murder on Monday.
OL,20,FThe Stewart brothers will be sentenced
OL,21,Fby Mrs Justice Cutts on Friday.
OL,26,@qD@AOUqD@NO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G7/10
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,375,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37408
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1783774107
OL,3,CTwo brothers facing life in jail over
OL,4,Cmurdering civil servant "for fun" in
OL,5,C1984
OL,7,FIn a statement, Mr Littler's cousin
OL,8,FPatricia McClure said: "I am
OL,9,Fparticularly angry these murderers
OL,10,Fhave had 42 years of freedom and they
OL,11,Fpicked Anthony at random for fun,
OL,12,Fwhile I am glad that people have been
OL,13,Ffound accountable."
OL,15,FMr Littler was "kind" with a "great
OL,16,Fsense of humour" but did not talk much
OL,17,Fabout his job because of the Official
OL,18,FSecrets Act, she said.
OL,26,@pD@XOUuD@SO]wD@POUwD@UO]wD@^OUxD@PO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G8/10
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,375,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37409
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1783774107
OL,3,CTwo brothers facing life in jail over
OL,4,Cmurdering civil servant "for fun" in
OL,5,C1984
OL,7,FMrs McClure said: "During this
OL,8,Finvestigation, I have seen a statement
OL,9,Ffrom my aunt. I found out Anthony
OL,10,Fwrote to his mother every week without
OL,11,Ffail.
OL,13,F"I am heartbroken for my aunt that she
OL,14,Fnever got the chance to find out what
OL,15,Freally happened to her son and police
OL,16,Finvestigations that followed leading
OL,17,Fto where we are now.
OL,19,F"She went to her grave never knowing
OL,20,Fthat people were held accountable for
OL,21,Fwhat happened.
OL,26,@oD@SOUuD@AOU{D@AOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G9/10
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,375,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37410
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1783774107
OL,3,CTwo brothers facing life in jail over
OL,4,Cmurdering civil servant "for fun" in
OL,5,C1984
OL,7,F"Anthony was an only child. We were
OL,8,Falways very close because of it.
OL,10,F"In conclusion, I would like to say I
OL,11,Fwas devastated by Anthony's murder. I
OL,12,Flost a great friend who was like a
OL,13,Fbrother to me."
OL,26,@oD@AOUrD@AOUuD@OO]
